select
 CUENTABANCO, DenominacionComercial, CodProcesadora ,  FECHAPROCESO, CodClient,
 Sucursal, SucursalBancard,  sum(y.resultado) AS MONTO
from                                                                                                               
(Select z.*,                                       
    case                                     
        when z.CRDB= 'D' then z.MONTO * -1           
        when z.CRDB = 'C' then z.MONTO                               
        else 0                               
    End Resultado                                           
from (SELECT     A.CDTIPMOV AS CRDB, A.CDIMPORT AS MONTO, A.CDCTABAN AS CUENTABANCO, b.gp77clisno as DenominacionComercial,
concat(CDCODNEG,CDDVCNEG ) as CodProcesadora , A.CDFECPRO AS FECHAPROCESO, b.gp77clicod as CodClient,
b.gp77cliSuc as Sucursal, d.ge03sucnom as SucursalBancard
from  QS36F.CLRD01PF A
JOIN GXPRDTA.GPT077 B on concat(CDCODNEG,CDDVCNEG ) = b.gp77codpro
JOIN GXGedta.get024 c on c.ge23clicod = b.gp77clicod and c.ge24clisuc = b.gp77clisuc
join gxgedta.get003 d on d.ge03succod = c.ge24succod  
where CDCTABAN in ('$vCta_Comercio$')
AND CDFECPRO = '$vFecha_Proceso$')Z)Y
GROUP BY     CUENTABANCO, FECHAPROCESO, CodProcesadora, CodClient, Sucursal,DenominacionComercial, SucursalBancard

select
 CUENTABANCO, DenominacionComercial, CodProcesadora ,  FECHAPROCESO, CodClient,
 Sucursal, SucursalBancard,  sum(y.resultado) AS MONTO
from                                                                                                               
(Select z.*,                                       
    case                                     
        when z.CRDB= 'D' then z.MONTO * -1           
        when z.CRDB = 'C' then z.MONTO                               
        else 0                               
    End Resultado                                           
from (SELECT     A.CDTIPMOV AS CRDB, A.CDIMPORT AS MONTO, A.CDCTABAN AS CUENTABANCO, b.gp77clisno as DenominacionComercial,
concat(CDCODNEG,CDDVCNEG ) as CodProcesadora , A.CDFECPRO AS FECHAPROCESO, b.gp77clicod as CodClient,
b.gp77cliSuc as Sucursal, d.ge03sucnom as SucursalBancard
from  QS36F.CLRD01PF A
JOIN GXPRDTA.GPT077 B on concat(CDCODNEG,CDDVCNEG ) = b.gp77codpro
JOIN GXGedta.get024 c on c.ge23clicod = b.gp77clicod and c.ge24clisuc = b.gp77clisuc
join gxgedta.get003 d on d.ge03succod = c.ge24succod  AND d.GE01EMPCOD = c.GE24EMPCOD
where CDCTABAN in ('$vCta_Comercio$')
AND CDFECPRO = '$vFecha_Proceso$' AND CDTIPCTA = '1')Z)Y
GROUP BY     CUENTABANCO, FECHAPROCESO, CodProcesadora, CodClient, Sucursal,DenominacionComercial, SucursalBancard

SELECT
    CUENTABANCO,
    DenominacionComercial,
    CodProcesadora,
    FECHAPROCESO,
    CodClient,
    Sucursal,
    SucursalBancard,
    MONTO,
    COUNT(*) OVER(PARTITION BY 1) AS ResultadosEncontrados
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            CDTIPCTA AS TIPODECUENTA,
            A.CDCTABAN AS CUENTABANCO,
            b.gp77clisno AS DenominacionComercial,
            CONCAT(CDCODNEG, CDDVCNEG) AS CodProcesadora,
            A.CDFECPRO AS FECHAPROCESO,
            b.gp77clicod AS CodClient,
            b.gp77cliSuc AS Sucursal,
            d.ge03sucnom AS SucursalBancard,
            SUM(A.CDIMPORT) AS MONTO
        FROM
            QS36F.CLRD01PF A
        JOIN GXPRDTA.GPT077 B ON
            CONCAT(CDCODNEG, CDDVCNEG) = b.gp77codpro
        JOIN GXGedta.get024 c ON
            c.ge23clicod = b.gp77clicod
            AND c.ge24clisuc = b.gp77clisuc
        JOIN gxgedta.get003 d ON
            d.ge03succod = c.ge24succod
            AND d.GE01EMPCOD = c.GE24EMPCOD
        WHERE
            CDCTABAN IN ('$vCta_Comercio$')
            AND CDFECPRO = '$vFecha_Proceso$'
        GROUP BY
            CDTIPCTA,
            A.CDCTABAN,
            b.gp77clisno,
            CONCAT(CDCODNEG, CDDVCNEG),
            A.CDFECPRO,
            b.gp77clicod,
            b.gp77cliSuc,
            d.ge03sucnom
    ) AS T
WHERE
    MONTO = '$vImporte$'
